room_title: Escape room "Tomb Of Doom" by House of Conundrum in Omaha
review: Tomb of Doom was amazing! The staff was so nice and accommodating. Couldn't stop talking about the experience even hours after we went! I will definitely be back!

room_title: Escape room "Tomb Of Doom" by House of Conundrum in Omaha
review: My family and I went this weekend having no idea what to expect. We did the Tomb of Doom first and had such an amazing time that we immediately did the Bat Cave after. I would definitely recommend to people that enjoy puzzling challenges!

room_title: Escape room "Tomb Of Doom" by House of Conundrum in Omaha
review: This was my first time. Went with my sister and brother in law. It was a blast - we did the Tomb of Doom. Will be doing this again.

room_title: Escape room "Tomb Of Doom" by House of Conundrum in Omaha
review: We had such a great time! It was our first time at an escape room and they did not disappoint! We chose The Tomb of Doom and we had a blast and will definitely be coming back!

room_title: Escape room "Tomb Of Doom" by House of Conundrum in Omaha
review: So fun! We did Tomb of Doom and it was so challenging and so much fun! We will definitely be back!
